data.title: William “Bottom Billy” Davis (1754
data.meta_description: William Davis Bottom Billy b. 11 March 1754, Shrewsbury, New Jersey; d. ca. 1834-1840 Clark or Shelby Co. Ohio; m. 1773 Elizabeth Havens, b. 1754 Shrewsbury, New Jersey; d. 1834 Clark Co. Ohio.  They lived in Washington Co., Pennsylvania 2 1/2 years and in Harrison Co.
